.DS_Store

# Local-only working artifacts — never commit
docs/superpowers/
**/IDEAS.md

# Behavior-measurement reports — generated per-run, vary by API, not committed
**/measurements/*/report.md

# Per-plugin development environments
plugins/*/.venv/
plugins/*/.pytest_cache/
plugins/*/__pycache__/
plugins/*/*/__pycache__/
plugins/*/*/*/__pycache__/

# Python bytecode caches anywhere in the tree
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Type-check / lint caches
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
